title: [XPX]Airports of Norway Enhanced X v2 for X-Plane 10
description:
This is the second version of my Airpots of Norway Enhanced X package for the X-Plane 10 flight simulator. Like the previous one, it include the freeware Airports of Norway 3.3 pack for FSX converted to work with X-Plane 10 with Aerosoft Oslo X for ENGM and freeware ENZV from the Org. But this second version now include a Svalbard mesh and a Svalbard airport with building and HDR Lighting, plus many more improvment.

This new version include: 

- HDR Lighting for ENGM, ENBR, ENSG, ENZV, ENCN, ENVA, ENTC and ENSB
- Building for ENSB and ENSG
- Cleaned version of Aerosoft Oslo X
- ENGM and ENZV optimized for HD Mesh v2

Enjoy !
